It's not a big deal.

4
00:01:40,107 --> 00:01:41,907
I just suffered some minor injuries.

5
00:01:41,907 --> 00:01:43,667
It's all my maid's fault

6
00:01:43,667 --> 00:01:45,627
to bother Minister and Madam Kudi.

7
00:01:46,267 --> 00:01:47,427
I'm so sorry.

8
00:01:53,427 --> 00:01:54,927
Minister is smart,

9
00:01:54,927 --> 00:01:56,847
and Lady Zhang is tolerant.

10
00:01:56,847 --> 00:01:58,787
It seems as if I failed to
teach my sister properly.

11
00:01:59,627 --> 00:02:00,987
Madam Kudi, don't say so.

12
00:02:01,507 --> 00:02:02,867
It's just a misunderstanding.

13
00:02:02,867 --> 00:02:03,936
Hypocritical.

14
00:02:30,592 --> 00:02:31,680
Whoa.

15
00:03:13,267 --> 00:03:14,368
Shouyue.

16
00:03:26,667 --> 00:03:27,747
How is the decree?

17
00:03:52,107 --> 00:03:53,184
Are you okay?

18
00:03:57,227 --> 00:03:58,272
The decree…

19
00:03:58,272 --> 00:03:59,328
General Cheng

20
00:03:59,867 --> 00:04:01,267
neglects in recovering
the thieves due to lingering,

21
00:04:01,267 --> 00:04:02,307
is reduced sentence and
relieved of official positions.

22
00:04:03,267 --> 00:04:06,507
Wang Wendu committed the crime of forging
imperial edicts, is sentenced death penalty,

23
00:04:07,147 --> 00:04:08,227
and would return to Chang'an
to await the final decision.

24
00:04:08,947 --> 00:04:11,507
The rest of the generals,
Zhou Zhidu and Su Haizheng,

25
00:04:12,507 --> 00:04:13,536
return to their respective departments,

26
00:04:15,667 --> 00:04:17,867
my mentor temporarily replaces
as the Chief Administrator

27
00:04:18,587 --> 00:04:19,616
to control the armed forces.

28
00:04:23,907 --> 00:04:24,992
Do you catch a cold?

29
00:04:27,987 --> 00:04:30,467
Didn't His Majesty mention the slaughter
of the merchants in the city?

30
00:04:31,027 --> 00:04:33,427
Why do Su Haizheng and his party
stay safe and sound?

31
00:04:37,827 --> 00:04:38,987
About the slaughter
of the merchants in the city,

32
00:04:39,827 --> 00:04:41,587
after all, it's bad for
Tang Dynasty's reputation,

33
00:04:42,987 --> 00:04:45,027
so there's no mention of it in the decree.

34
00:04:46,016 --> 00:04:47,104
The law does not punish the masses.

35
00:04:47,667 --> 00:04:50,667
There's no way to convict everyone involved.

36
00:04:51,968 --> 00:04:53,024
Therefore,

37
00:04:53,547 --> 00:04:56,307
Cheng Zhijie and Wang Wendu
were severely punished,

38
00:04:57,027 --> 00:04:58,208
the generals were dismissed,

39
00:04:58,987 --> 00:05:00,787
and my mentor was assigned.

40
00:05:01,827 --> 00:05:02,880
The implication

41
00:05:03,648 --> 00:05:04,704
is clear.

42
00:05:08,307 --> 00:05:10,667
Since your mentor stays to
act as the Chief Administrator,

43
00:05:11,387 --> 00:05:13,847
does His Majesty intend
to prepare for war again

44
00:05:13,847 --> 00:05:14,867
to fight Helu?

45
00:05:18,627 --> 00:05:20,427
I have discussed this matter
with my mentor all night.

46
00:05:21,547 --> 00:05:23,147
If we want to pacify the north
in one fell swoop,

47
00:05:24,307 --> 00:05:26,307
it's not about the number of soldiers,
but their excellence.

48
00:05:27,827 --> 00:05:29,024
Therefore,

49
00:05:29,024 --> 00:05:31,307
the great army will return east as planned,

50
00:05:33,307 --> 00:05:36,587
only the elite soldiers chosen
from the border troops for strict training.

51
00:05:38,507 --> 00:05:39,967
No one can match my mentor

52
00:05:39,967 --> 00:05:41,187
in training and preparing for war

53
00:05:41,187 --> 00:05:42,387
and charging into battle.

54
00:05:43,067 --> 00:05:46,587
But he is a little lax in managing soldiers

55
00:05:46,587 --> 00:05:47,587
and food provision.

56
00:05:49,408 --> 00:05:50,496
Liuli.

57
00:05:51,907 --> 00:05:54,187
I'm afraid I have to spend more time in camp

58
00:05:54,987 --> 00:05:56,160
after that.

59
00:06:00,768 --> 00:06:01,824
I have to

60
00:06:02,347 --> 00:06:03,947
pack up and go to the military camp later.

61
00:06:05,747 --> 00:06:07,807
You have a good rest at home.

62
00:06:07,807 --> 00:06:09,147
There are many affairs this year,

63
00:06:09,867 --> 00:06:11,787
and there will only be
more and more afterwards.

64
00:06:13,347 --> 00:06:15,507
You don't have to go if you don't want to.

65
00:06:16,947 --> 00:06:18,048
Anyway, in Xizhou,

66
00:06:18,867 --> 00:06:20,467
no one dares to trouble you.

67
00:06:22,587 --> 00:06:23,627
After this incident,

68
00:06:24,147 --> 00:06:25,827
with you and your mentor,

69
00:06:25,827 --> 00:06:28,587
Su Nanjin would not dare to
come and make trouble again.

70
00:06:29,307 --> 00:06:32,027
And Qu Chongyu will not
find us trouble anymore.

71
00:06:32,587 --> 00:06:35,147
Am I bluffing by association?

72
00:06:37,627 --> 00:06:39,227
Yes, you are.

73
00:06:43,187 --> 00:06:44,587
That Qu Chongyu,

74
00:06:44,587 --> 00:06:46,427
although he is somewhat narrow-minded,

75
00:06:46,427 --> 00:06:48,547
he's also manly.

76
00:06:49,507 --> 00:06:52,807
He thought I would
rob the Qu family of their power

77
00:06:52,807 --> 00:06:53,987
and force them back to Chang'an,

78
00:06:54,787 --> 00:06:55,947
now the knot is settled.

79
00:06:57,267 --> 00:06:59,947
I think if anything happens
in Xizhou in the future,

80
00:07:00,467 --> 00:07:02,907
given his character,
he will surely offer his help.

81
00:07:58,272 --> 00:07:59,360
Tan.

82
00:08:00,027 --> 00:08:01,267
Look who he looks like.

83
00:08:05,027 --> 00:08:06,587
He looks like the Kitchen God
painted by My lady.

84
00:08:15,547 --> 00:08:17,427
Minister, you are here. I'll take you in.

85
00:08:19,147 --> 00:08:20,224
Okay, thank you.

86
00:08:20,827 --> 00:08:21,952
Here, take it.

87
00:08:27,008 --> 00:08:28,128
Hurry up.

88
00:08:28,128 --> 00:08:29,187
Wait for me.

89
00:08:29,187 --> 00:08:30,587
Come here.

90
00:08:30,587 --> 00:08:32,927
My lady, you have painted
so many Kitchen Gods these days.

91
00:08:32,927 --> 00:08:34,507
All were given to the neighbors.

92
00:08:35,147 --> 00:08:37,507
Today is the 23rd of the twelfth lunar month,
the day for offering sacrifices to Kitchen God.

93
00:08:37,507 --> 00:08:39,107
We still have to do the painting ourselves.

94
00:08:42,187 --> 00:08:44,027
Sister.

95
00:08:45,187 --> 00:08:46,304
Look who's here.

96
00:08:48,576 --> 00:08:49,600
Madam.

97
00:09:07,987 --> 00:09:09,216
Please take a seat, Minister.

98
00:09:24,147 --> 00:09:25,184
Madam.

99
00:09:28,587 --> 00:09:31,387
Madam, this is
the cotton workshop's bonus for this year.

100
00:09:32,947 --> 00:09:34,787
Thank you, Minister, for remembering this.

101
00:09:35,467 --> 00:09:36,707
It's no big deal.

102
00:09:36,707 --> 00:09:38,087
Without you,

103
00:09:38,087 --> 00:09:39,527
there wouldn't be this cotton workshop.

104
00:09:39,527 --> 00:09:40,667
I should do so.

105
00:09:46,827 --> 00:09:49,147
Actually, I come here
to deal with a matter today.

106
00:09:51,307 --> 00:09:52,607
The Senior Official Pei

107
00:09:52,607 --> 00:09:53,827
always does good deeds
to the surrounding villages.

108
00:09:54,507 --> 00:09:57,947
There are dozens of village junior officers
specially coming to Xizhou,

109
00:09:57,947 --> 00:09:59,136
wanting to…

110
00:10:00,107 --> 00:10:02,307
But heard that the Senior Official is away,

111
00:10:03,267 --> 00:10:07,067
then they want to pay respects to his wife.

112
00:10:07,067 --> 00:10:09,267
There's no reason to bother you

113
00:10:09,267 --> 00:10:10,707
with such a trivial matter.

114
00:10:11,307 --> 00:10:12,667
But…

115
00:10:12,667 --> 00:10:15,387
They came through a long trip
here in the cold winter,

116
00:10:15,387 --> 00:10:17,887
I took it upon myself to leave them
at the Protector-General's Mansion.

117
00:10:17,887 --> 00:10:18,944
Minister.

118
00:10:20,307 --> 00:10:22,047
My sister is not feeling well these days,

119
00:10:22,047 --> 00:10:24,147
she hasn't had a proper meal,

120
00:10:24,147 --> 00:10:25,387
hasn't even stepped outside.

121
00:10:34,667 --> 00:10:36,027
I'm not that delicate.

122
00:10:36,027 --> 00:10:37,747
It's just a trip
to the Protector-General's Mansion.

123
00:10:38,947 --> 00:10:40,427
I can't keep the village junior officers
waiting too long.

124
00:10:40,987 --> 00:10:42,987
Ni, take fifty copies
of the Buddhist scriptures.

125
00:10:42,987 --> 00:10:44,288
You come along with me.

126
00:10:44,288 --> 00:10:45,347
Yes.

127
00:10:45,347 --> 00:10:46,528
Then I'll go with you.

128
00:10:52,667 --> 00:10:53,728
Madam, please.

129
00:11:01,587 --> 00:11:02,827
Sister.

130
00:11:02,827 --> 00:11:04,187
You're not feeling well,

131
00:11:04,187 --> 00:11:05,367
don't force yourself.

132
00:11:05,367 --> 00:11:06,528
I am okay.

133
00:11:19,616 --> 00:11:20,704
Madam is here.

134
00:11:24,107 --> 00:11:25,248
Madam is here.

135
00:11:28,384 --> 00:11:29,387
Hello, Madam.

136
00:11:29,387 --> 00:11:30,432
Hello Madam.

137
00:11:35,307 --> 00:11:37,227
Madam, do you still remember me?

138
00:11:37,227 --> 00:11:39,927
My several daughters-in-law
always think of you, Madam.

139
00:11:39,927 --> 00:11:41,987
They deliberately made
some pairs of shoes and socks.

140
00:11:41,987 --> 00:11:43,787
Hope you don't mind them crude.

141
00:11:45,347 --> 00:11:47,327
My spouse is always thinking of you,

142
00:11:47,327 --> 00:11:48,887
prepared some local products for you.

143
00:11:48,887 --> 00:11:50,747
Hope you don't mind them.

144
00:11:51,264 --> 00:11:52,327
Yes.

145
00:11:52,327 --> 00:11:53,587
We have gifts too.

146
00:11:53,587 --> 00:11:55,027
Please take them.

147
00:11:56,787 --> 00:11:58,107
Thank you all for your kindness.

148
00:11:58,707 --> 00:12:00,467
Then I and Shouyue would take them.

149
00:12:01,027 --> 00:12:03,887
However, I have also prepared some small gifts.

150
00:12:03,887 --> 00:12:06,507
I also hope that you do not refuse.

151
00:12:12,107 --> 00:12:13,216
Thank you, Madam.

152
00:12:15,392 --> 00:12:16,747
- Thank you, Madam.
- Yes.

153
00:12:16,747 --> 00:12:18,147
Thank you, Madam.

154
00:12:18,147 --> 00:12:19,200
Thank you, Madam.

155
00:12:21,664 --> 00:12:28,320
[Protector-General's Mansion]

156
00:12:29,227 --> 00:12:30,547
Thank you for today, Madam.

157
00:12:30,547 --> 00:12:32,127
With you personally show up,

158
00:12:32,127 --> 00:12:33,987
village junior officers will
return home content.

159
00:12:35,947 --> 00:12:37,056
Sister.

160
00:12:37,056 --> 00:12:38,112
I'm fine.

161
00:12:38,667 --> 00:12:39,727
Please stop, Minister.

162
00:12:39,727 --> 00:12:40,987
We shall take our leave now.

163
00:12:41,627 --> 00:12:43,347
I should take you back.

164
00:12:51,227 --> 00:12:52,867
- My lady.
- Sister.

165
00:12:53,547 --> 00:12:55,547
- Sister.
- Madam.

166
00:12:56,704 --> 00:12:57,867
- My lady.
- Madam.

167
00:12:57,867 --> 00:12:59,187
- Sister.
- Madam.

168
00:13:14,267 --> 00:13:16,027
My lady began to tremble.

169
00:13:17,147 --> 00:13:18,272
What should we do?

170
00:13:19,827 --> 00:13:20,827
Sister's hands are so cold.

171
00:13:24,307 --> 00:13:25,867
The doctors all have checked the pulse,

172
00:13:25,867 --> 00:13:27,427
why hasn't a result been discussed yet?

173
00:13:27,947 --> 00:13:30,067
What's the treatment? I'm really worried.

174
00:13:30,907 --> 00:13:32,067
You guys stay here.

175
00:13:32,067 --> 00:13:33,167
I'll go urge them.

176
00:13:33,167 --> 00:13:34,208
Okay.

177
00:13:40,987 --> 00:13:42,927
This symptom is very obvious.

178
00:13:42,927 --> 00:13:44,327
Cold and heat are alternating.

179
00:13:44,327 --> 00:13:46,147
It is the stagnation of qi.

180
00:13:46,147 --> 00:13:47,947
It's also the disease of qi stagnation.

181
00:13:47,947 --> 00:13:49,707
We should regulate the qi now.

182
00:13:49,707 --> 00:13:51,307
Mr. Hua, I don't think so.

183
00:13:51,307 --> 00:13:53,647
It is clear that the patient
has the internal heat.

184
00:13:53,647 --> 00:13:55,667
We should let her sweat now.

185
00:13:55,667 --> 00:13:56,672
You are right.

186
00:13:56,672 --> 00:13:58,027
I have been a doctor for many years.

187
00:13:58,027 --> 00:13:59,427
We should regulate the qi now.

188
00:13:59,427 --> 00:14:01,567
Mr. Hua, I think you're missing the point here.

189
00:14:01,567 --> 00:14:03,207
It is clear that the patient
has the internal heat.

190
00:14:03,207 --> 00:14:04,507
How can you do so?

191
00:14:04,507 --> 00:14:06,747
Have you come up with any results?

192
00:14:06,747 --> 00:14:08,487
My lady's getting cold again.

193
00:14:08,487 --> 00:14:10,347
When can the right medicine be prescribed?

194
00:14:18,027 --> 00:14:19,547
Can you really cure her or not?

195
00:14:19,547 --> 00:14:20,587
Do you know how to treat her?

196
00:14:21,707 --> 00:14:23,467
Minister, of course.

197
00:14:24,027 --> 00:14:25,667
It is clear that the patient
has the internal heat.

198
00:14:25,667 --> 00:14:27,387
Just let it out and she'll be okay.

199
00:14:28,827 --> 00:14:30,187
Minister.

200
00:14:30,187 --> 00:14:31,547
It is clear that qi should be regulated.

201
00:14:32,147 --> 00:14:33,827
No need to let the heat out.

202
00:14:35,667 --> 00:14:36,768
Physician Han.

203
00:14:37,888 --> 00:14:38,976
What do you think?

204
00:14:50,907 --> 00:14:52,467
Madam has symptoms of a cold.

205
00:14:53,147 --> 00:14:54,747
Now is the time of heat and cold alternating.

206
00:14:55,907 --> 00:14:57,187
I'm afraid

207
00:14:58,107 --> 00:14:59,547
she'll faint by night.

208
00:14:59,547 --> 00:15:00,727
So the urgent need

209
00:15:00,727 --> 00:15:02,907
is to facilitate the flow of qi
and disperse the cold.

210
00:15:04,347 --> 00:15:05,440
If it's too late,

211
00:15:10,467 --> 00:15:11,488
it will be incurable.

212
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:23,987
Come on, hurry.

213
00:15:24,707 --> 00:15:27,547
Unfortunately, my brother-in-law
has gone to General Su's camp,

214
00:15:27,547 --> 00:15:29,587
and there's no one in the family
to make decisions.

215
00:15:29,587 --> 00:15:31,167
With Sister being so ill,

216
00:15:31,167 --> 00:15:32,707
what should we do?

217
00:15:32,707 --> 00:15:33,792
When My lady fainted,

218
00:15:33,792 --> 00:15:36,027
Minister Qu has already sent
someone to deliver a letter to Master.

219
00:15:36,027 --> 00:15:38,467
Master should be on his way back by now.

220
00:15:50,507 --> 00:15:51,927
How old are you?

221
00:15:51,927 --> 00:15:54,267
How dare you make such a false statement!

222
00:15:54,267 --> 00:15:56,587
Although Madam's symptoms
of cold are a bit serious,

223
00:15:56,587 --> 00:15:58,107
they are not hard to treat.

224
00:15:58,107 --> 00:16:01,267
It's improbable for a cold
to progress this rapidly.

225
00:16:02,907 --> 00:16:05,147
Has Madam been weak and sensitive to cold?

226
00:16:05,147 --> 00:16:07,227
Did she have a heavy headache
the last few days,

227
00:16:07,787 --> 00:16:09,227
then lost her appetite,

228
00:16:09,747 --> 00:16:11,147
and today has also caught a bit of cold?

229
00:16:12,067 --> 00:16:13,827
Exactly, Physician Han.

230
00:16:14,347 --> 00:16:16,347
Although My lady looks weak,

231
00:16:16,347 --> 00:16:17,867
she has never been sick.

232
00:16:19,907 --> 00:16:22,387
Could it be that you have misdiagnosed?

233
00:16:22,387 --> 00:16:24,827
Her problem is that she never gets sick.

234
00:16:36,627 --> 00:16:38,787
H-He is so arrogant.

235
00:16:52,747 --> 00:16:54,027
Three qian of Angelica sinensis.

236
00:16:54,867 --> 00:16:56,327
Three qian of Cassia twig.

237
00:16:56,327 --> 00:16:58,007
Three qian of Peony.

238
00:16:58,007 --> 00:16:59,827
Two qian of honey-fried licorice.

239
00:16:59,827 --> 00:17:01,247
Two qian of Polyporus.

240
00:17:01,247 --> 00:17:03,427
25 pieces of jujube.

241
00:17:04,267 --> 00:17:07,507
Madam is suffering from high fever
and still using this hot medicine.

242
00:17:08,787 --> 00:17:10,547
Truly, quack doctors are killing.

243
00:17:11,947 --> 00:17:13,007
Yes.

244
00:17:13,007 --> 00:17:14,387
Is it that you

245
00:17:14,387 --> 00:17:17,227
have treated cattle and sheep often?

246
00:17:23,307 --> 00:17:25,307
Senior Official Pei is like my father to me.

247
00:17:25,824 --> 00:17:26,944
I am not knowledgeable.

248
00:17:27,747 --> 00:17:28,987
Perhaps I cannot save Madam.

249
00:17:29,667 --> 00:17:31,127
But if follow their treatment,

250
00:17:31,127 --> 00:17:32,527
Madam will surely have no chance of survival.

251
00:17:32,527 --> 00:17:34,667
You… Well…

252
00:17:38,347 --> 00:17:39,627
Lady boss.

253
00:17:39,627 --> 00:17:41,067
Please trust me this time.

254
00:17:41,627 --> 00:17:43,847
Boil the prescription to one liter
with three liters of water

255
00:17:43,847 --> 00:17:45,347
and hurry let Madam take it.

256
00:17:45,347 --> 00:17:46,467
If it's wrong,

257
00:17:47,267 --> 00:17:49,147
I will bear any punishment.

258
00:17:50,667 --> 00:17:52,467
Okay, I will listen to you.

259
00:17:53,027 --> 00:17:54,067
But no matter what,

260
00:17:54,067 --> 00:17:55,347
we must save Lady Liuli's life.

261
00:17:57,107 --> 00:17:58,208
Ni.

262
00:17:59,547 --> 00:18:01,067
Boil the medicine according to the recipe now.

263
00:18:01,707 --> 00:18:02,720
Hurry up.

264
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,904
Yes.

265
00:18:12,667 --> 00:18:13,747
I take my leave.

266
00:18:19,347 --> 00:18:20,544
I take my leave.

267
00:18:28,704 --> 00:18:29,760
Physician Han.

268
00:18:31,307 --> 00:18:32,607
Are you sure

269
00:18:32,607 --> 00:18:33,947
you can cure Madam?

270
00:18:37,987 --> 00:18:39,136
I have seen

