305
00:21:42,987 --> 00:21:44,407
Without seeing any improvement in Madam,

306
00:21:44,407 --> 00:21:46,307
I really can't put my mind at ease.

307
00:21:48,067 --> 00:21:49,827
That's what I wanted to tell you.

308
00:21:50,667 --> 00:21:51,827
I have asked Physician Han,

309
00:21:52,507 --> 00:21:54,227
the cold that Sister suffered today

310
00:21:54,227 --> 00:21:55,487
is merely an introduction.

311
00:21:55,487 --> 00:21:57,127
Sister is weak and sensitive to cold,

312
00:21:57,127 --> 00:21:59,507
and her spirit is weakened
and harmed by fatigue.

313
