324
00:22:28,387 --> 00:22:30,647
Sister had a serious illness
in her early years.

325
00:22:30,647 --> 00:22:32,947
She failed to be taken care and caught a chill.

326
00:22:35,427 --> 00:22:36,587
Lady Yunyi is right.

327
00:22:42,387 --> 00:22:43,867
Back when she was in the palace,

328
00:22:43,867 --> 00:22:46,067
Prince Cao wanted to use Lady Liuli
to frame the Crown Prince,

329
00:22:46,067 --> 00:22:47,232
so he poisoned her.

330
00:22:47,867 --> 00:22:49,147
Lady Liuli once became
seriously ill for several months.

331
00:22:50,147 --> 00:22:52,647
It was the miraculous medicine that
Shouyue found after enduring hardships,

332
00:22:52,647 --> 00:22:53,987
to finally save Lady Liuli's life.

333
00:22:55,467 --> 00:22:56,867
So Madam hasn't been

334
00:22:57,467 --> 00:22:59,127
to a doctor since the illness,

335
00:22:59,127 --> 00:23:00,147
and she hasn't had any care.

336
00:23:03,467 --> 00:23:04,787
The current condition of Madam,

337
00:23:04,787 --> 00:23:07,267
she'd be better if she occasionally falls ill.

338
00:23:07,267 --> 00:23:09,507
Her problem is that she never falls ill.

339
00:23:10,547 --> 00:23:12,707
She hangs on with her sheer willpower.

340
00:23:13,227 --> 00:23:14,547
Once she is relieved,

341
00:23:15,267 --> 00:23:16,907
then illness would strike her.

342
00:23:19,427 --> 00:23:21,987
Not to mention Lady Liuli has spent
these years in the palace in constant anxiety,

343
00:23:22,667 --> 00:23:24,147
even after marrying Shouyue,

344
00:23:24,147 --> 00:23:25,667
she can't make any mistake,

345
00:23:25,667 --> 00:23:27,307
nor dare to be careless
or negligent at any time.

346
00:23:28,347 --> 00:23:29,827
It turns out that Lady Liuli
is not someone who won't get sick,

347
00:23:30,507 --> 00:23:32,387
but that she can't get sick
and dare not get sick.

348
00:23:33,747 --> 00:23:35,427
And now it's all settled,

349
00:23:36,227 --> 00:23:38,147
and she has to pay back everything she owed.

350
00:23:39,747 --> 00:23:41,067
Physician Han.

351
00:23:41,067 --> 00:23:42,907
Is there anything else we can do for my sister?

352
00:23:43,507 --> 00:23:44,827
The current condition of Madam,

353
00:23:44,827 --> 00:23:46,587
it's not the fever to fear, but the chills.

354
00:23:46,587 --> 00:23:48,427
The worst thing is
the exhaustion from sweating.

355
00:23:49,067 --> 00:23:51,107
You should prepare
hot water bags to keep her warm.

356
00:23:51,907 --> 00:23:54,427
Once the cold reaches the elbows and knees,

357
00:23:54,427 --> 00:23:55,787
come to tell me immediately.

358
00:23:56,507 --> 00:23:57,947
Okay, thank you, Physician Han.

359
00:24:01,427 --> 00:24:03,947
I have sent messengers twice
to deliver letters to Senior Official Pei,

360
00:24:03,947 --> 00:24:05,187
I'm sure he'll be back soon.

361
00:24:05,867 --> 00:24:06,947
I'll just wait here.

362
00:24:06,947 --> 00:24:09,247
Keep me informed on anything.

363
00:24:09,247 --> 00:24:10,336
Okay.

364
00:24:11,827 --> 00:24:12,867
Thank you, Physician Han.

365
00:24:48,547 --> 00:24:50,107
My sister's high fever has not recurred,

366
00:24:50,667 --> 00:24:52,387
but her hands and feet have remained cold,

367
00:24:52,387 --> 00:24:54,107
which reaches the elbows and knees.

368
00:24:54,107 --> 00:24:55,347
What should we do now?

369
00:25:01,627 --> 00:25:02,907
I'll get Physician Han right away.

370
00:25:05,107 --> 00:25:06,267
I can't feed her.

371
00:25:06,987 --> 00:25:09,107
My lady's hands and feet
are getting colder and colder.

372
00:25:09,107 --> 00:25:10,707
What should we do?

373
00:25:12,467 --> 00:25:14,947
Sister, can you hear me?

374
00:25:15,587 --> 00:25:16,667
Can you take the medicine?

375
00:25:17,427 --> 00:25:19,667
If you don't take it, you can't get better.

376
00:25:30,688 --> 00:25:31,808
Physician Han.

377
00:25:53,507 --> 00:25:55,947
Physician Han, how is my sister's condition?

378
00:25:59,427 --> 00:26:00,448
Physician Han.

379
00:26:05,627 --> 00:26:07,127
Is there anything we can do to save her?

380
00:26:07,127 --> 00:26:09,347
Physician Han, I beg you.

381
00:26:09,347 --> 00:26:11,987
Do something to save My lady.

382
00:26:46,827 --> 00:26:49,267
Now Sister's face is paler.

383
00:26:49,267 --> 00:26:50,667
Her limbs are all cold.

384
00:26:51,307 --> 00:26:52,727
We've added up to three quilts

385
00:26:52,727 --> 00:26:54,427
and put several hot water bags.

386
00:26:54,427 --> 00:26:56,487
But she could not stop shivering,

387
00:26:56,487 --> 00:26:58,247
and her body is slowly curling up.

388
00:26:58,247 --> 00:26:59,547
I wrote a new prescription.

389
00:27:00,187 --> 00:27:04,047
It's just licorice, rhizoma zingiberis,
fresh ginger and aconite.

390
00:27:04,047 --> 00:27:05,967
