394
00:27:09,627 --> 00:27:11,367
You need to think of something else.

395
00:27:11,367 --> 00:27:12,387
If it's a man,

396
00:27:13,307 --> 00:27:15,667
moxibustion can be used to warm him up,

397
00:27:16,307 --> 00:27:17,307
then massage him and give medicine.

398
00:27:23,147 --> 00:27:25,107
Then use it. What are you waiting for?

399
00:27:27,387 --> 00:27:29,547
Physician Han, is there any difficulty?

400
00:27:32,307 --> 00:27:33,312
