401
00:27:37,787 --> 00:27:39,067
It requires the clothes to be removed.

402
00:27:51,227 --> 00:27:52,327
Why are you still hesitating?

403
00:27:52,327 --> 00:27:53,787
Sister's life is at stake.

404
00:27:53,787 --> 00:27:55,147
What worldly etiquette

405
00:27:55,147 --> 00:27:56,727
