415
00:28:48,467 --> 00:28:49,536
Physician Han.

416
00:28:50,507 --> 00:28:51,648
Is there anything else you can do?

417
00:28:58,067 --> 00:29:00,107
We can try moxibustion.

418
00:29:00,707 --> 00:29:01,707
Physician Han, please give it a try.

