00:32:56,512 --> 00:32:57,600
That's great.

464
00:32:58,427 --> 00:32:59,467
Go and give Madam her medicine.

465
00:32:59,467 --> 00:33:00,544
Okay.

466
00:33:16,747 --> 00:33:17,856
She has taken it.

467
00:33:28,627 --> 00:33:29,824
Go bring a cup of warm water.

468
00:33:30,707 --> 00:33:31,744
She says it's spicy.

469
00:33:32,387 --> 00:33:33,600
Okay.

470
00:33:35,667 --> 00:33:36,800
Here.

471
00:33:38,528 --> 00:33:39,584
Slow down.

472
00:33:46,747 --> 00:33:48,707
