My lady's condition will recur,

473
00:33:48,707 --> 00:33:50,467
so you might have to stay at the mansion

474
00:33:51,027 --> 00:33:52,667
to treat My lady at any time.

475
00:33:54,627 --> 00:33:56,907
Sorry about any inconvenience, Physician Han.

476
00:33:57,427 --> 00:33:58,547
If you want anything,

477
00:33:58,547 --> 00:33:59,947
just tell me.

478
00:33:59,947 --> 00:34:01,067
Lady Ni, you are welcome.

479
00:34:01,667 --> 00:34:03,107
Then I won't disturb your rest.

480
00:34:13,587 --> 00:34:14,927
You must be hungry after all this work.

481
00:34:14,927 --> 00:34:17,107
Beef noodles, eat it while it's hot.

482
00:34:17,107 --> 00:34:18,147
Eat before you rest.

483
00:34:22,067 --> 00:34:23,107
Y-Your hand…

484
00:34:26,907 --> 00:34:28,307
I-I'll apply medicine for you.

485
00:34:28,307 --> 00:34:29,547
That's not a big deal.

486
00:34:31,267 --> 00:34:32,947
It's so swelling.

487
00:34:39,907 --> 00:34:41,152
Please take a seat.

488
00:35:00,707 --> 00:35:02,907
I didn't even see you blush when
you were doing moxibustion to Lady Liuli.

489
00:35:06,747 --> 00:35:07,947
Now you are applying medicine to my hand,

490
00:35:08,467 --> 00:35:09,507
why are you so blushing?

491
00:35:10,747 --> 00:35:12,387
T-That's different.

492
00:35:13,587 --> 00:35:14,987
I am a doctor.

493
00:35:14,987 --> 00:35:16,187
When I am treating,

494
00:35:16,187 --> 00:35:18,827
I only think of the symptoms,
without any distractions.

495
00:35:19,947 --> 00:35:21,907
To me, Madam is just a patient.

496
00:35:25,056 --> 00:35:26,080
What about me?

497
00:35:31,227 --> 00:35:32,320
Am I not a patient?

498
00:35:32,867 --> 00:35:33,987
Isn't this an injury?

499
00:35:35,648 --> 00:35:38,187
I-I can't argue with you.

500
00:35:38,747 --> 00:35:40,947
Anyway…

501
00:35:42,467 --> 00:35:43,667
you are not the same as Madam.

502
00:36:36,507 --> 00:36:38,787
