for coming to visit Madam.

503
00:36:38,787 --> 00:36:41,407
But Madam is still asleep.

504
00:36:41,407 --> 00:36:42,827
The Senior Official is accompanying her.

505
00:36:43,507 --> 00:36:46,147
It is not convenient for us outsiders
to enter the house and disturb.

506
00:36:47,027 --> 00:36:49,467
It would be better for me to talk to you.

507
00:36:50,187 --> 00:36:51,387
Wait until Madam wakes up,

508
00:36:51,387 --> 00:36:52,747
we can visit together.

509
00:36:54,427 --> 00:36:56,027
I'm afraid I'm the only one outsider

510
00:36:56,027 --> 00:36:57,867
who is not convenient
to enter the house and disturb.

511
00:36:58,387 --> 00:37:00,987
Even you can help
host guests at the mansion now.

512
00:37:00,987 --> 00:37:02,227
Then Madam Kudi

513
00:37:02,227 --> 00:37:03,447
has long considered you

514
00:37:03,447 --> 00:37:05,147
and Lady Yunyi as sisters now.

515
00:37:06,227 --> 00:37:07,987
What are you talking about?

516
00:37:08,507 --> 00:37:10,947
I am just living close
to the Senior Official's mansion,

517
00:37:10,947 --> 00:37:13,387
so I am more convenient to visit Madam.

518
00:37:14,507 --> 00:37:16,267
I was just kidding.

519
00:37:16,267 --> 00:37:17,667
There's no need to take it seriously.

520
00:37:18,547 --> 00:37:19,567
By the way,

521
00:37:19,567 --> 00:37:21,667
I am indeed curious about something.

522
00:37:22,507 --> 00:37:25,527
We all know Lady Yunyi is
the younger sister of Madam Kudi.

523
00:37:25,527 --> 00:37:28,227
I wonder whether she is
a cousin or a paternal cousin.

524
00:37:29,947 --> 00:37:31,947
Could it be that Yunyi's surname also is Kudi?

525
00:37:35,507 --> 00:37:38,227
I wonder why you care about this.

526
00:37:39,507 --> 00:37:41,007
Envy, of course.

527
00:37:41,007 --> 00:37:43,227
Madam Kudi treats Lady Yunyi kindly.

528
00:37:43,227 --> 00:37:46,107
I also want to be closer to Madam Kudi.

529
00:37:47,587 --> 00:37:49,587
This is a family matter for Madam Kudi.

530
00:37:50,387 --> 00:37:51,787
I can't talk about it.

531
00:37:51,787 --> 00:37:54,067
Let's drink tea and eat the fruit.

532
00:37:55,147 --> 00:37:56,507
Just casual chat.

533
00:37:57,227 --> 00:37:58,787
You are being so careful.

534
00:37:59,307 --> 00:38:00,867
No wonder Madam Kudi trusts you.

535
00:38:21,947 --> 00:38:22,976
Sister Liu.

536
00:38:22,976 --> 00:38:24,387
Yunyi.

