00:38:24,387 --> 00:38:26,427
Thanks to you going there for me,

538
00:38:26,427 --> 00:38:28,627
I am most impatient to talk
to that Zhang Minniang.

539
00:38:28,627 --> 00:38:30,067
I don't want her bothering my sister.

540
00:38:30,947 --> 00:38:32,707
Yunyi, in my opinion,

541
