547
00:38:43,427 --> 00:38:44,587
I don't want to talk to her either.

548
00:38:45,627 --> 00:38:46,707
That would be for the best.

549
00:38:46,707 --> 00:38:48,967
You are pure, in order to
keep from falling into her trap,

550
00:38:48,967 --> 00:38:50,187
